===============================================================================
= Variants:
===============================================================================

* var[1234]ref: 
    * Reference serial code.
    * Pure C code.

* var[1234]a:
    * Same as var[1234]ref.
    * Code optimized to reduce the cost of indexing.

* var[1234]b:
    * Same as var[1234]ref.
    * Modified to use BLAS routines.

